{"name": "minto", "metadata": {"name": "minto", "version": "0.9.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: MacOS", "Operating System :: POSIX", "Operating System :: POSIX :: Linux", "Operating System :: Unix", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3 :: Only", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://www.j-ij.com/", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": "https://jij-inc.github.io/minto", "dependencies": ["numpy", "pandas", "pydantic", "jijzept", "jijmodeling"], "summary": "Experiment management and benchmark tools for mathematical optimization", "upload_time": 1733202659}, "documentation": ["\n# MINTO: Jij Management and Insight tool for Optimization\n\n[![PyPI version shields.io](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/minto.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/minto/)\n[![PyPI pyversions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/minto.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/minto/)\n[![PyPI implementation](https://img.shields.io/pypi/implementation/minto.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/minto/)\n[![PyPI format](https://img.shields.io/pypi/format/minto.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/minto/)\n[![PyPI license](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/minto.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/minto/)\n[![PyPI download month](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/minto.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/minto/)\n[![Downloads](https://pepy.tech/badge/minto)](https://pepy.tech/project/minto)\n\n[![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/Jij-Inc/minto/graph/badge.svg?token=ZhfvFdt1sJ)](https://codecov.io/gh/Jij-Inc/minto)\n\n\n`minto` is a Python library designed for developers working on research and development or proof-of-concept experiments using mathematical optimization. Positioned similarly to mlflow in the machine learning field, `minto` provides features such as saving optimization results, automatically computing benchmark metrics, and offering visualization tools for the results.\n\nPrimarily supporting Ising optimization problems,  plans to extend its support to a wide range of optimization problems, such as MIP solvers, in the future.\n\n## Installation\n`minto` can be easily installed using pip.\n\n``` shell\npip install minto\n```\n\n## Documentation and Support\n\nDocumentation: https://jij-inc.github.io/minto/\n\nTutorials will be provided in the future. Stay tuned!\n\n\n## How to Contribute\n\nSee [CONTRIBUITING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) \n\n---\n\nCopyright (c) 2023 Jij Inc.\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "minto.typing", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "minto.typing.ArtifactDataType", "type": {"name": "TypeAlias", "xref": {"fqname": "typing_extensions.TypeAlias", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "minto.io", "documentation": ["`io` module is used to handle load/save operations.\n\nModules:\n    save: save module is used to save data to disk.\n    load: load module is used to load data from disk."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "minto.consts", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "minto.io.load", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "minto.io.load.load", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "experiment_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "savedir", "type": {"name": "str | pathlib.Path", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Experiment", "xref": {"fqname": "minto.experiment.experiment.Experiment", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "minto.consts.default", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "minto.consts.default.D